# Google Identity Services OAuth client id — REQUIRED to sign in.
#
# Sign-in is the only way into the app, and it goes entirely through Google.
# Without this value the "Continue with Google" button stays disabled.
#
# Create a client id at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   1. Create (or pick) a project.
#   2. Configure the OAuth consent screen.
#   3. Create credentials → "OAuth client ID" → Web application.
#   4. Add your dev origin (e.g. http://localhost:5173) to
#      "Authorized JavaScript origins".
#   5. Copy the generated client id below.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and fill in the value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
